# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MEDINA — EXCLUSIONES SOVEREIGNAE
# "Quod non pertinet, non committitur." (What does not belong is not committed.)
#
# Custom ignore rules for the Medina platform.
# Covers: ICP/Motoko, Node.js, Rust, Browser Extensions, Distribution.
#
# TRACKED (never ignored):
#   dist/          — install scripts, bundler, standalone download page
#   docs/          — GitHub Pages (download page + worker)
#   scripts/       — native build/validate/deploy scripts
#   extensions/    — 20 browser extension source directories
#   packages/      — SDK source packages
#   organism-cli/  — terminal AI source
#
# Attribution: Alfredo Medina Hernandez | Medina Tech | Dallas, TX
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Release bundler writes here (node dist/bundle.js)
build/

# ── Rust (medina_crypto) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# cargo build/check output
target/
# Lock file regenerated per machine
Cargo.lock

# ── Node.js (organism-cli, packages/*) ────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
# Package manager locks — regenerated per install
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# ── ICP / dfx (canister builds) ──────────────────────────────────────────
.dfx/
canister_ids.json

# ── OS files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ── Editor state ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Runtime / temp ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.pid
*.seed

# ── Python ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
